metadata.name: TSUYOSHI SHINJO Graphics #001
metadata.description:
2021年11月4日札幌市内。新庄剛志による、北海道日本ハムファイターズ監督就任記者会見。ワインレッドカラーの鮮やかなスーツ姿で登場。「ファイターズを変えていきたいし、僕がプロ野球を変えていきたい」と所信表明し、日本中の話題の中心に。
 November 4, 2021, Sapporo—Tsuyoshi Shinjo's inaugural press conference as the director of the Hokkaido Nippon-Ham Fighters. Appeared in a bright wine-red suit. He expressed his belief that "I want to change the Fighters and I want to change professional baseball," and became the center of attention throughout Japan.
